high_descs: turn around, walk to face the toilet
pick up the pink bar of soap from the red garbage can
turn right, walk to face the sinks
put the soap in the right sink basin, wash with water, pick up soap from sink basin
back up to face the sinks along with the cabinets underneath sinks
open the third cabinet door from the left, place soap in the bottom of cabinet, close door
anns.task_desc: wash soap and put away in bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the red bin on the floor.
Take the bar soap out of the bin.
Turn right and walk towards the sink far from you.
Place the soap in the sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Take a step to the left to find the cabinet in between the two sinks.
Place the bar soap in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the washed bar soap from the red bin into the cabinet below the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go straight to face the red waste basket between the toilet and sink.
Pick up the soap from out of the red waste basket.
Move to the right to face the double sinks.
Place the soap in the sink to the right, run the water, then pick the soap up.
Move to the left to face the sink on the left.
Open the left door on the cabinet below the right sink, place the soap inside of it and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the soap in the cabinet below the right sink.
